entries.femaleVariant: "Electronic Murderer," I got one word – masterpiece. Didn't quite click till that last scene...
Then boom! All the pieces came together!
The heroine, it was 'cause of her outdated optics model she got hacked!
Little bit of horror, little bit sci-fi. Perfect combo.
The bodies were never there! That netrunner was feeding her hallucinations.
It broke her down, she couldn't take it – took to the noose.
Bottom line – keep current on your chrome. Think we've been in her shoes, haha.
